channel.title: Run Sever problem
channel.description: Hello Moparscape, I have a quick question. When I run my run-server.bat file it keeps on saying "Server is already in use." I have portforward correctly (it was running fine before). I have placed my ip in gui.java in the client folder. Any other ideas?

item.title: Run Sever problem
item.dc:creator: @Untrimmed Untrimmed
item.description:
@Untrimmed wrote:

Wow thank you I would have never guessed that. It actually turned out to be Utorrent it was just snapped to my tray. Thanks so much!

item.title: Run Sever problem
item.dc:creator: @Clawz_fury lare69
item.description:
@Clawz_fury wrote:

Something on your computer is occupying the port you are trying to run your server on; if you have something like utorrent open, terminate it.
